12
00:02:09,190 --> 00:02:10,520
He must kneel on one knee,

13
00:02:11,120 --> 00:02:12,160
hand the ring

14
00:02:12,160 --> 00:02:13,990
and say loads of cheesy lines.

15
00:02:13,990 --> 00:02:15,200
The crowd would cheer for them

16
00:02:15,200 --> 00:02:16,310
and say,

17
00:02:16,310 --> 00:02:17,940
"Marry him, marry him!"

18
00:02:19,670 --> 00:02:20,910
What does it have to do with them?

19
00:02:20,910 --> 00:02:22,190
It's none of their businesses.

20
00:02:23,030 --> 00:02:24,400
Marriage is supposed to be

21
00:02:24,400 --> 00:02:25,040
