24
00:02:28,400 --> 00:02:29,240
When did it

25
00:02:29,240 --> 00:02:30,080
become a fancy show?

26
00:02:30,950 --> 00:02:32,360
Proposing in public

27
00:02:32,400 --> 00:02:33,750
