28
00:02:33,750 --> 00:02:35,630
to force the other one to say yes.

29
00:02:35,630 --> 00:02:37,200
It's too arrogant to be romantic.

30
00:02:37,440 --> 00:02:38,240
It's just for show.

31
00:02:50,070 --> 00:02:51,830
Are these people enough?

32
00:02:52,760 --> 00:02:54,600
Who else can I invite?

33
00:02:56,470 --> 00:02:57,870
Give it another thought.

34
00:02:59,080 --> 00:03:00,630
Both parties are willing.

35
00:03:02,040 --> 00:03:03,080
Think about it,

36
00:03:03,350 --> 00:03:04,480
the grass,

37
00:03:04,480 --> 00:03:05,910
the balloons,

38
00:03:05,910 --> 00:03:07,040
the curtains.

39
00:03:07,350 --> 00:03:08,520
And...

40
00:03:09,720 --> 00:03:10,840
And…

41
00:03:11,710 --> 00:03:12,550
Candles.

42
00:03:14,910 --> 00:03:15,590
Candles.

43
00:03:15,750 --> 00:03:17,430
In a dark room,

44
00:03:17,430 --> 00:03:18,800
candles are arranged

45
00:03:18,840 --> 00:03:20,190
in the shape of a heart.

46
00:03:20,550 --> 00:03:22,160
So are the balloons.

47
00:03:22,510 --> 00:03:23,070
Right!

48
00:03:23,110 --> 00:03:24,150
The rose petals should be arranged

49
00:03:24,150 --> 00:03:25,230
in the shape of heart, as well.

50
00:03:26,000 --> 00:03:26,960
That's so cheesy.

51
00:03:27,790 --> 00:03:29,680
[Daily special offers! A special gift for your loved one at 26.66 yuan!]

52
00:03:29,920 --> 00:03:31,070
So people

53
00:03:31,070 --> 00:03:32,390
need these for a proposal.

54
00:03:36,790 --> 00:03:39,070
These are not important.

55
00:03:39,070 --> 00:03:40,279
What's important is

56
00:03:40,310 --> 00:03:42,800
the love behind the surprise.

57
00:03:45,120 --> 00:03:46,670
That's important, of course,

58
00:03:46,670 --> 00:03:47,430
but it's bad that

59
00:03:47,430 --> 00:03:48,710
the surprise turns into a shock.

60
00:03:50,790 --> 00:03:51,960
There's a man

61
00:03:52,310 --> 00:03:53,350
who hid the ring

62
00:03:53,390 --> 00:03:54,720
in a piece of cake for the proposal.

63
00:03:54,720 --> 00:03:56,040
But his girlfriend swallowed the ring

64
00:03:56,040 --> 00:03:57,590
while eating the cake.

65
00:03:57,590 --> 00:03:59,190
If the ring's stuck in her windpipe,

66
00:03:59,190 --> 00:04:00,440
it will be such a tragedy.

67
00:04:02,350 --> 00:04:03,520
Another guy

68
00:04:04,240 --> 00:04:05,240
hid the ring

69
00:04:05,240 --> 00:04:05,920
in his wound.

70
00:04:06,080 --> 00:04:06,760
Then he went to

71
00:04:06,760 --> 00:04:07,830
his girlfriend who's a nurse

72
00:04:07,830 --> 00:04:08,760
to get it out.

73
00:04:08,800 --> 00:04:10,120
Just picture it.

74
00:04:10,680 --> 00:04:12,640
His girlfriend picked the ring out of

75
00:04:12,840 --> 00:04:14,750
the bloody wound

76
