with tweezers.

77
00:04:20,790 --> 00:04:24,740
[Shocking! A Russian man hid a wedding ring inside his belly wound!]

78
00:04:21,840 --> 00:04:23,560
A Russian man

79
00:04:23,870 --> 00:04:26,550
hid his proposal ring

80
00:04:26,550 --> 00:04:28,120
in a wound on his belly

81
00:04:28,120 --> 00:04:29,400
and proposed to his girlfriend?

82
00:04:31,280 --> 00:04:32,320
How could he do this?

83
00:04:33,470 --> 00:04:34,510
How creative.

84
00:04:35,880 --> 00:04:36,870
Lu Fangning!

85
00:04:39,990 --> 00:04:40,920
What?

86
00:04:41,430 --> 00:04:42,440
Wait,

87
00:04:42,440 --> 00:04:43,480
you two asked me here

88
00:04:43,480 --> 00:04:44,870
to enjoy your cooking.

89
00:04:44,870 --> 00:04:45,670
Where is the food?

90
00:04:46,200 --> 00:04:47,280
In the end,

91
00:04:47,280 --> 00:04:49,230
all I have is an unpeeled apple.

92
00:04:49,760 --> 00:04:50,750
What's going on

93
00:04:50,750 --> 00:04:51,840
with you two?

94
00:04:51,990 --> 00:04:53,190
Why are you asking me so many things

95
00:04:53,190 --> 00:04:54,030
about proposal now?

96
00:04:54,030 --> 00:04:54,950
What happened?

97
00:04:57,600 --> 00:04:59,040
I...

98
00:04:59,070 --> 00:05:00,960
-She has a proposal scene!
-She writes about a proposal!

99
00:05:05,560 --> 00:05:06,960
That made sense.

100
00:05:09,190 --> 00:05:10,600
Ms. Lu.

101
00:05:27,430 --> 00:05:30,120
That came out of nowhere.

102
00:05:30,790 --> 00:05:32,710
Not to mention they gave strange answers.

103
00:05:34,390 --> 00:05:36,680
They specifically asked me

104
00:05:37,110 --> 00:05:37,990
about proposals…

105
00:05:39,120 --> 00:05:40,070
And Ling Rui…

106
00:05:44,640 --> 00:05:46,630
Didn't I say yes ages ago?

107
00:05:46,630 --> 00:05:47,720
This is unnecessary.

108
00:05:48,000 --> 00:05:49,680
I don't need this romantic ceremony.

109
00:05:49,680 --> 00:05:50,880
It's a waste of money.

110
00:05:58,720 --> 00:06:00,030
What should I do?

111
00:06:06,950 --> 00:06:07,790
Welcome home.

112
00:06:10,200 --> 00:06:11,120
What are you doing?

113
00:06:12,470 --> 00:06:14,440
I was just searching for some information online.

114
00:06:15,240 --> 00:06:16,390
About what? Let me see it.

115
00:06:16,560 --> 00:06:17,360
It's for the hospital.

116
00:06:17,360 --> 00:06:18,110
It's very boring.

117
00:06:18,310 --> 00:06:18,950
Let me have a look.

118
00:06:19,150 --> 00:06:20,190
There's nothing to see. Let it go.

119
00:06:20,190 --> 00:06:21,600
You are acting too suspicious.

120
00:06:21,600 --> 00:06:22,680
-Don't be so stingy!
-I told you.

121
00:06:22,680 --> 00:06:23,720
It's nothing.

122
00:06:23,720 --> 00:06:24,920
Just forget it.

123
00:06:25,510 --> 00:06:26,200
Trust me.

124
00:06:26,710 --> 00:06:28,830
You're overreacting.

125
00:06:30,360 --> 00:06:31,110
Are you messaging someone?

126
00:06:31,480 --> 00:06:32,830
No. Who would I message anyone?

127
00:06:32,830 --> 00:06:34,750
Let me see it. Just a sneak peek.

128
00:06:35,240 --> 00:06:36,280
-Listen to me.
-Just let me have a look.

129
00:06:36,550 --> 00:06:37,230
Your phone.

130
00:06:37,430 --> 00:06:38,270
Phone.

131
00:06:39,510 --> 00:06:40,880
I can check your phone. Give it to me.

132
00:06:40,880 --> 00:06:42,510
Your phone is ringing.

133
00:06:42,510 --> 00:06:43,950
Answer the call.

134
00:06:46,359 --> 00:06:47,800
I'll question you later.

135
00:06:50,510 --> 00:06:51,440
Hello?

136
00:06:53,960 --> 00:06:55,200
The police station?

137
00:06:58,510 --> 00:07:01,810
[Deer Sing]

138
00:07:03,440 --> 00:07:05,150
What do I know about art parks?

139
00:07:05,430 --> 00:07:06,030
I just mentioned it

140
00:07:06,600 --> 00:07:07,560
to someone

141
00:07:07,560 --> 00:07:08,400
from Ming Cheng,

142
00:07:08,710 --> 00:07:09,550
he did the job

143
00:07:09,550 --> 00:07:10,280
for me voluntarily.

144
00:07:11,160 --> 00:07:12,270
I won't let Lu Fangning

145
00:07:12,880 --> 00:07:13,920
do business here.

146
00:07:15,870 --> 00:07:16,400
Mr. Gao,

147
00:07:17,350 --> 00:07:18,480
did I do a great job?

148
00:07:19,710 --> 00:07:20,600
I'm serving justice

149
00:07:20,910 --> 00:07:21,950
for both of us.

150
00:07:23,760 --> 00:07:25,440
Very good. Well done.

151
00:07:26,680 --> 00:07:27,470
I didn't expect

152
00:07:27,470 --> 00:07:29,110
even when Lu Fangning's gone,

153
00:07:29,710 --> 00:07:31,120
she could still help me

154
00:07:31,390 --> 00:07:32,710
quell a treacherous

155
00:07:33,600 --> 00:07:34,120
employee.

156
00:07:35,590 --> 00:07:36,070
Mr. Gao.

157
00:07:38,550 --> 00:07:39,560
I was only

158
00:07:39,960 --> 00:07:41,160
trying to find out

159
00:07:41,270 --> 00:07:43,150
who used me as their scapegoat.

160
00:07:44,960 --> 00:07:46,080
Who knows?

161
00:07:46,080 --> 00:07:48,070
Manager Yang, impressive work.

162
00:07:48,070 --> 00:07:49,910
You secretly handed over

163
00:07:49,910 --> 00:07:50,920
Deer Sing Group's

164
00:07:50,950 --> 00:07:52,230
outlet and manufacturer

165
00:07:52,230 --> 00:07:52,800
tenders

166
00:07:52,800 --> 00:07:54,710
to Ming Cheng.

167
00:07:56,630 --> 00:07:57,910
The projects, amounts,

168
00:07:57,910 --> 00:07:58,990
and details are all here.

169
00:07:59,440 --> 00:08:01,030
Manager Yang, please have a closer look.

170
00:08:01,030 --> 00:08:01,960
If I wronged you

171
00:08:01,960 --> 00:08:03,040
with any of the charges,

172
00:08:03,350 --> 00:08:04,230
I could help you

173
00:08:04,230 --> 00:08:05,430
reduce the amount of compensation.

174
00:08:12,630 --> 00:08:13,160
By the way,

175
00:08:14,030 --> 00:08:15,390
how's your son doing lately?

176
00:08:17,030 --> 00:08:18,910
As the saying goes,

177
00:08:18,910 --> 00:08:19,950
the fish begins to rot

178
00:08:20,680 --> 00:08:21,560
at the head.

179
00:08:29,790 --> 00:08:30,430
Give HR a call.

180
00:08:30,430 --> 00:08:31,550
They can handle the rest.

181
00:08:32,350 --> 00:08:33,960
Fire him, fined him, and make it a public announcement.

182
00:08:34,320 --> 00:08:34,960
Do it now.

183
00:08:35,240 --> 00:08:36,150
Don't make me repeat myself.

184
00:08:36,590 --> 00:08:37,320
Yes, Mr. Gao.

185
00:08:39,160 --> 00:08:40,390
Those jerks.

186
00:08:40,440 --> 00:08:41,830
How dare they hurt my delicate arm!

187
00:08:43,470 --> 00:08:46,080
Fortunately, justice is never late.

188
00:08:46,080 --> 00:08:47,950
They are finally arrested.

189
00:08:49,830 --> 00:08:50,859
What's wrong?

190
00:08:51,859 --> 00:08:52,680
They've got caught.

191
00:08:52,680 --> 00:08:53,830
Why do you still look upset?

192
00:08:55,160 --> 00:08:56,150
I'm happy.

193
00:08:56,600 --> 00:08:57,590
And someone else

194
00:08:57,590 --> 00:08:58,790
is going to pay for his medical bill.

195
00:08:58,790 --> 00:09:00,070
It doesn't count as work injuries.

196
00:09:01,280 --> 00:09:02,990
I know you're mean with your words.

197
00:09:02,990 --> 00:09:04,240
You still care about me, right?

198
00:09:04,270 --> 00:09:05,840
That's enough. I don't care.

199
00:09:05,990 --> 00:09:07,760
You're worried about my arm, right?

200
00:09:07,760 --> 00:09:08,200
Come on.

201
00:09:11,430 --> 00:09:12,470
My arm!

202
00:09:13,880 --> 00:09:14,680
This is the precious arm

203
00:09:14,680 --> 00:09:15,800
that makes you money.

204
00:09:16,030 --> 00:09:17,000
Otherwise,

205
00:09:17,070 --> 00:09:17,880
why did you confront

206
00:09:17,880 --> 00:09:19,030
your enemy for me?

207
00:09:21,840 --> 00:09:23,030
However,

208
00:09:23,030 --> 00:09:24,600
I think you got the wrong guy.

209
00:09:28,870 --> 00:09:30,440
I can confront him as I please.

210
00:09:31,320 --> 00:09:33,400
I don't need a reason.

211
00:09:45,070 --> 00:09:46,270
[It seems like]

212
00:09:46,350 --> 00:09:46,950
[you've]

213
00:09:46,950 --> 00:09:48,230
[stooped very low while I was away.]

214
00:09:48,790 --> 00:09:50,160
I didn't know

215
00:09:50,550 --> 00:09:51,680
you were such a lousy person

216
00:09:51,920 --> 00:09:53,520
who would resort to petty tricks.

217
00:09:56,560 --> 00:09:57,190
Do you think

218
00:09:57,190 --> 00:09:58,030
you're the most pitiful

219
00:09:58,030 --> 00:09:59,790
and the greatest person alive?

220
00:09:59,790 --> 00:10:00,630
Is that why you think

221
00:10:00,630 --> 00:10:01,390
we must play along

222
00:10:01,390 --> 00:10:02,840
with your overdramatic story?

223
00:10:19,070 --> 00:10:20,080
I've warmed some milk for you.

224
00:10:20,350 --> 00:10:21,040
Drink it.

225
00:10:21,120 --> 00:10:21,880
Thank you.

226
00:10:25,120 --> 00:10:25,960
That's all?

227
00:10:37,390 --> 00:10:38,230
What's wrong?

228
00:10:39,840 --> 00:10:41,480
The problems are all solved.

229
00:10:41,840 --> 00:10:43,160
The park is ready for businesses.

230
00:10:43,160 --> 00:10:44,670
Don't worry about it.

231
00:10:45,040 --> 00:10:45,790
Have some rest.

232
00:10:48,110 --> 00:10:49,440
I just think

233
00:10:49,950 --> 00:10:51,190
I've wronged him.

234
00:10:53,150 --> 00:10:54,240
When did you ever regret

235
00:10:54,240 --> 00:10:55,430
scolding others?

236
00:10:56,870 --> 00:10:58,350
I don't

237
00:10:58,350 --> 00:10:59,320
regret it at all!

238
00:11:00,360 --> 00:11:02,190
What I said when I scolded him

239
00:11:02,190 --> 00:11:02,950
was all reasonable.

240
00:11:02,990 --> 00:11:03,520
You know that.

241
00:11:04,200 --> 00:11:05,350
I might have been

242
00:11:05,350 --> 00:11:06,480
a little harsh on him.

243
00:11:06,840 --> 00:11:08,910
But essentially, I wasn't wrong.

244
00:11:10,680 --> 00:11:11,480
You're so naughty.

245
00:11:15,920 --> 00:11:16,870
What was that for?

246
00:11:18,080 --> 00:11:20,600
Stopping you from overthinking.

247
00:11:21,030 --> 00:11:21,950
Especially from

248
00:11:21,950 --> 00:11:23,350
thinking about another man.

249
00:11:25,310 --> 00:11:28,160
You consider Gao Erfan a man?

250
00:11:28,190 --> 00:11:29,510
You're still thinking about him?

251
00:11:29,510 --> 00:11:30,200
I…

252
00:11:31,190 --> 00:11:32,120
What about now?

253
00:11:32,590 --> 00:11:33,630
-And now?
-No. No.

254
00:11:35,150 --> 00:11:35,990
Who should you be thinking?

255
00:11:38,070 --> 00:11:38,870
I am

256
00:11:39,280 --> 00:11:39,950
thinking about Youyou.

257
00:11:41,190 --> 00:11:42,110
Youyou's asleep.

258
00:11:42,750 --> 00:11:43,710
It's useless to think about him.

259
00:11:45,190 --> 00:11:46,200
Then…

260
00:11:46,200 --> 00:11:47,440
I'm warning you.

261
00:11:47,880 --> 00:11:49,160
Think carefully before you answer.

262
00:11:51,910 --> 00:11:52,440
I think about you.

263
00:12:02,070 --> 00:12:04,040
Are you sure Youyou is asleep?

264
00:12:27,680 --> 00:12:32,140
[Gao Erfan]

265
00:13:01,800 --> 00:13:02,710
[I'm Ling Rui.]

266
00:13:03,190 --> 00:13:04,590
[Fangning's birthday is two days from now.]

267
00:13:05,510 --> 00:13:06,910
[You were the one Lu Yue loved most.]

268
00:13:07,630 --> 00:13:09,030
[I hope you could attend the party for her.]

269
00:13:25,430 --> 00:13:26,840
This one could do.

270
00:13:26,870 --> 00:13:28,350
It's full of bling.

271
00:13:28,350 --> 00:13:30,230
It suits Fangning's style.

272
00:13:30,670 --> 00:13:31,240
Sir.

273
00:13:31,240 --> 00:13:32,790
May I help you?

274
00:13:33,160 --> 00:13:34,640
I want to order this cake.

275
00:13:34,640 --> 00:13:35,600
Sorry, sir,

276
00:13:35,430 --> 00:13:39,290
[Blisscake]

277
00:13:35,600 --> 00:13:37,390
we're low in stock of this cake.

278
00:13:37,390 --> 00:13:38,230
Besides, the last one

279
00:13:38,230 --> 00:13:39,440
had already been ordered.

280
00:13:39,470 --> 00:13:40,990
Could you make another one?

281
00:13:40,990 --> 00:13:42,830
I'm afraid we can't finish it by tomorrow.

282
00:13:44,040 --> 00:13:45,040
Well, let me explain

283
00:13:45,040 --> 00:13:45,960
the situation to you.

284
00:13:46,600 --> 00:13:47,310
My buddy

285
00:13:47,310 --> 00:13:47,950
finally

286
00:13:47,950 --> 00:13:49,080
asked me for help.

287
00:13:49,080 --> 00:13:50,360
I must finish the task

288
00:13:50,390 --> 00:13:51,200
with perfection.

289
00:13:51,200 --> 00:13:52,710
Otherwise, I would fail him.

290
00:13:52,710 --> 00:13:53,960
Maybe you could

291
00:13:53,960 --> 00:13:55,510
give me the number of the customer

292
00:13:55,510 --> 00:13:56,240
who ordered the cake.

293
00:13:56,280 --> 00:13:57,190
I could talk to him.

294
00:13:57,190 --> 00:13:58,190
Maybe he would let me have it.

295
00:13:58,190 --> 00:13:59,000
Sorry, sir.

296
00:13:59,000 --> 00:14:00,150
Our policies forbid us

